Name: Russian manicure
Description:
A dry high end manicure with precise cuticle work. 
A clean and crisp cuticle with the effect of less regrowth.

Name: Luxury manicure
Description:
Spoil yourself by upgrading to our luxury manicure.
This service includes 
- Russian manicure cuticle work (gel needs to be booked separately)
- Hand scrub
- Hand soak 
- Hand massage

(Please note this is a service with out gel application - if you would like gel additionally please add on separately)

Name: Dual form gel extensions
Description:
For the long nail girls wanting a secure, long strong extension. 
Dual forms are a hard gel extension, which means this is a file off product

Name: BIAB extensions  (builder in a bottle)
Description:
Biab extensions are a builder gel that extend your natural length. 
To kickstart your Biab journey, you can have longer nails from the start! 

Please note you can not add too much length with BIAB extensions as with extensions they are less durable- unlike long natural biab nails- they may not last as long as shorter extensions.

Name: Shellac manicure
Description:
Shellac on the top of natural nails. 
Lasts 2-3 weeks before needing a removal.

Description: Soak off gel nails (hands or toes)

Description: Soak off acrylic previously applied by steph

Name: LVL Lash Lift
Description:
SKIN TEST REQUIRED! 
LVL stands for length, volume and lift.
One way to think of a lash lift is like a perm for your eyelashes. Unlike a lash extension, a lash lift simply alters the shape and color of your natural lashes. 
Results last 6-8 weeks !

Name: HD Brow Sculpt
Description:
PATCH TEST REQUIRED  
Brow Sculpt is brow lamination with a bespoke HD Brows twist. Whether you dream of achieving that full, fluffy eyebrow look, want to create symmetry in uneven brows or tame unruly hairs, our BrowSculpt brow lamination treatment is for you.
WAX AND TINT INCLUDED

Name: Brow Lamination
Description:
PATCH TEST REQUIRED  
A perming technique to manipulate hairs into a new desired position 
WAX AND TINT NOT INCLUDED

Description: Eyebrow tint and shaping using wax for a clean crisp brow
